title: 2 Br 2 Ba Manufactured Home! For Rent In El Cajon
posting_body: This is a very nice 2 Bedroom 2 Bath split floor plan home located in the 5-Star community of Lakefront.
All appliances convey to the home.
Very open floor plan with Laminate floors.
Both bathrooms have been updated and the home has been kept in impeccable condition.
This home has a great outdoor area for those comfortable California mornings and evenings.
Nice size deck for your enjoyment.
Located At 9395 Harritt Rd Space 132 the community features 2 heated swimming pools for year-round swimming.
Basketball courts, BBQ areas, Exercise Room, Billiard room, and even a car wash.
Please call to schedule a viewing of this home.
It won't last at this price.
Close to all schools, shopping, and only 25 minutes from downtown San Diego and the beaches and airport.
